args: This is the fifth reconnaissance android\nthat has been destroyed while on patrol.\nI surmise there is an assailant.

▷Seems that way. But why is it only
going after combat androids?◁
Unknown. At present, I lack the data
to make more than wild speculation.
A child! Where did you come from?\n▷Weird. I didn't notice her either.◁
▷Uh, it's actually pretty dangerous here,\nso you should maybe hurry home?◁
Nooo. We wanna play more.\nIsn't that right, Aya?
That's right, Oto—we haven't played\nenough at all. It's time for tag.
Okay, then we'll be ＂it＂ and play with\nthat one there. Does that sound good?
A lovely idea, Aya. We'll chase the puppet,\nand if we catch it, I'll pop its head off!
Kya ha ha! And when you do,\nI'll give it a huge kick!
It would be wonderful to find all the heads\nwe've taken so far and line them up.

▷No way... This can't be!◁
There is a high probability these two
children are responsible for disabling
the other androids.
Ding ding ding! Alas, you figured it out\ntoo late, you unsightly wretch.
▷Why would a pair of kids like you\neven DO something like that?!◁
Kya ha ha! Did you hear that, Oto?\nHe wants to know WHY?!
Eh heh heh... This android certainly does\nsay some stupid things, Aya.
It's so STUPID to ask about reasons!\nBut I suppose that is to be expected\nfrom an unsightly little puppet.
Yes, stupid puppets just follow the\norders of whoever made them.
Kya ha ha! Oh, we know you, Laxi.
Eh heh heh. And we know you, Mascula.
You are an unsightly android with two\nhearts in one body. HE told us this.
We're the polar opposite of you!\nKyaaaa ha ha ha ha!
▷Why did you attack our friends?\nWhat is your goal?◁
*sigh* So stupid. That's a puppet for you.
I don't have a ＂goal.＂ ＂Goals＂ are for\nunsightly people who don't know\nwhat freedom is.
We met HIM, and now we are free.\nThat is why we no longer need goals.
▷So you just attacked our friends\nfor no reason?!◁
Looking at them annoyed us.\nDoes that count as a reason?
Yeah, we just got real mad at you things\nalways misunderstanding what freedom is!
You're all the same: Just a bunch of little\npuppets jumping whenever that Maestro\nperson tells you to jump.
Incorrect. Maestro gave us a heart and\nthe ability to choose our own actions\nbased on free judgment and will.
Kya ha ha! You can't be free if you depend\non a heart someone else gave you!
Yes, that heart controls all you do.\nPoor wittle puppets.
I deny that. I... I won't... You are enemies.\nCommencing termination.\n▷Laxi, wait!◁
Oh my! The puppet looks to act.\nHas someone cut your strings?
I heard someone was targeting androids,\nbut it can't be these kids, can it?
So this is the new Maestro? Eh heh heh.
Kya ha ha! This is SO funny!\nOne puppet controlling another?\nIt makes me LAUGH!

None of you know real freedom. From the
moment you were born, you've had your
stupid dreams and ideals and goals tying
you up in knots.
You're constrained and don't even know it!
Your freedom is but a mummer's show.\nOUR freedom is the true one!

Freedom bound up in ideals and goals is
a mistake. You say you're free, and yet
you let your dreams lead you about
by the nose.
Which means OUR freedom is right.\nAll others are but restrictive imitations.

How unsightly it is to labor under the
delusion that the manipulations of your
heart amount to freedom... Now permit
us to show you the real thing!
▷Even if you deny someone else's\nfreedom, it doesn't affirm your own.◁

The notion of a ＂correct＂ freedom is
base egotism and immature thinking.
You are simply biased when it comes
to the subject of freedom.

And YOU are just some THING,
so don't talk to us about freedom!
...Enough of this. Let's just show
them the truth of the world, Oto!
Good idea, Aya! We'll smash her body,\ngouge out her stupid false ＂heart,＂\nand use it to go BOWLING!
Only then will you reject the boring ideals\nand stupid goals some loser planted inside\nyou and see what true freedom it.
Living with someone pulling your strings\nis awful, so let us give you a front-row\nseat to a new way of existence!
I know that barrier...\nThese kids are...
We are wings. Paired, free,\nsoaring over all. We...are Agito!
Kyaaaa ha ha ha!\nEh heh heh heh!\nC'mon! Let's PLAY!
